t, drip email campaigns, transaction management, document storage, and an AI writing assistant. The AI features (added in 2024) help draft emails, create social posts, and answer client questions. While not as sophisticated as Lofty or Follow Up Boss's AI capabilities, Wise Agent's AI is practical and integrates naturally into the existing workflow. For solo agents earning under $100K/year who need a solid CRM without enterprise pricing, Wise Agent is frequently the best choice."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-green-400","children":"Pros"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-1.5","children":[["$","li","Exceptional value at $49/month — all-in-one for solo agents",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Exceptional value at $49/month — all-in-one for solo agents"]}],["$","li","Unlimited contacts and emails — no per-contact pricing surprises",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Unlimited contacts and emails — no per-contact pricing surprises"]}],["$","li","24/7 customer support included",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentCo